            "id": "https://ruyunjian.github.io/2026/03/23/Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/",
            "url": "https://ruyunjian.github.io/2026/03/23/Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/",
            "title": "Cpp笔记总结S1",
            "date_published": "2026-03-23T09:18:03.000Z",
            "content_html": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\assets\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><h3 id=\"一string类型\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#一string类型\">#</a> 一.string类型</h3>\n<hr>\n<p>1.求长度：arr.length()或者是arr.size()</p>\n<p>2.字符串的连接可以直接使用+号，形如c=a+b（eg：a=hello,b=world,c=a+b=hello world）</p>\n<p>3.=和普通变量一样赋值，但是是拷贝的副本</p>\n<h3 id=\"二for循环与auto迭代器\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#二for循环与auto迭代器\">#</a> <strong>二.for循环与auto迭代器</strong></h3>\n<hr>\n<p>1.auto可以转化为任意数据类型(eg:string a=&quot;abc&quot;;auto b=a;)</p>\n<p>2.定义一个数组arr[]，有如下语法：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-c++\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">int</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> arr</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">[</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">5</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">]</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">1</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">2</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">3</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">4</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">5</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">for</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">auto</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> x</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">    cout</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">x</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">endl</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>可以依次打印数组中的元素，输出结果就是12345，代替了三分号的步骤</p>\n<h3 id=\"三引用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#三引用\">#</a> 三,引用</h3>\n<hr>\n<p>引用就是<em>取别名</em> ，具体如下</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-c++\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">int</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> a</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">10</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">int</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> &#x26;</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">p</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">a</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">P </span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">+=</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 5</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">cout</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">a</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">endl</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>此时的输出结果为<code>a=15</code>,也就是说P在发生改变时a也会同时发生改变，就是相当于a的别名为p</p>\n<h3 id=\"四常用库函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#四常用库函数\">#</a> <strong>四.常用库函数</strong></h3>\n<hr>\n<p>I.<code>reverse翻转</code></p>\n<p>假定有一个vector容器储存的arr，则</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-c++\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">reverse（</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">begin</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">end</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">）</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>可以倒转整个vector容器</p>\n<p>II.<code>unique去重</code></p>\n<p>作用是去除容器或数组中相邻元素的重复出现的元素，返回值是去重之后的尾地址</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-c++\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">int</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> m</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">unique（</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">begin</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">end</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">）</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">-</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">begin</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> //m返回的是去重后的元素个数</span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>需要重点注意的是，<em>unique去重的是相邻元素的重复元素，而不是整个容器或数组中的重复元素，所有使用unique的时候一般要对整个容器或者数组进行sort排序（见下文）</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>III.sort排序</p>\n<p>1.sort排序是类似于快速排序的一种排序方式，时间复杂度为n*log2(n),执行效率比较高，一般首选sort</p>\n<p>2.sort的使用方法<br>\nsort含有三个参数sort（begin,end,cmp）,其中begin为指向待sort（）的数组的首元素的指针，end为指向待sort（）的数组的<em>尾元素的下一位指针</em>（不是尾元素，是尾元素的下一位！！）</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>cmp：自定义排序函数，返回bool类型，是一个布尔值函数</p>\n<p><code>bool</code> 是 C++ 的<strong>布尔类型</strong>，只有两个取值：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>true</code>（真，等价于 1）</li>\n<li><code>false</code>（假，等价于 0）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>bool 函数的核心作用：<strong>返回判断结果</strong>（是 / 否、对 / 错）</p>\n<h3 id=\"正确写法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#正确写法\">#</a> ✅ 正确写法</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>升序：<code>return a &lt; b</code></li>\n<li>降序：<code>return a &gt; b</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"绝对不能写\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#绝对不能写\">#</a> ❌ 绝对不能写</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>return a &lt;= b</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>return a &gt;= b</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>bool 函数就是只返回 true 或 false</strong></p>\n<p><code>a &lt; b</code> 本身，<strong>本来就是一个布尔表达式</strong>，若a &lt; b，则true，否则返回false</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"五容器基础笔记备份\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#五容器基础笔记备份\">#</a> <strong>五.容器基础&amp;&amp;笔记备份</strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/../Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/1cb363a0240a849696a7f6457744f77a.jpg\" alt></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/1266b250bbd962a3cfe02aff6bc8d1f3.jpg\" alt=\"1266b250bbd962a3cfe02aff6bc8d1f3\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/3849496e2a9d9cba41a99d5295dff58c.jpg\" alt=\"3849496e2a9d9cba41a99d5295dff58c\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/bfe508c05447f35fae53d0425c5c8e50.jpg\" alt=\"bfe508c05447f35fae53d0425c5c8e50\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/../Cpp%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93S1/ef88628f71026bd26ec4c808558360b6.jpg\" alt=\"ef88628f71026bd26ec4c808558360b6\"></p>\n",
